<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>On the picket line</b></font></P>
<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">May 2, 2003 | Page 11</font></p>


<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><B><P>OTHER STORIES BELOW:<BR></B>
